{% comment %}
  LP — Size Guide (B2C landing page)

  Code-only LP element. Edit this file to change copy or step images.
  Not editable through the Shopify theme editor by design.

  Step images live on the Shopify CDN. Update URLs inline to swap them.
  The "Consulta la tabella taglie" button opens the size-guide popup
  that ships inside lp-offerta (triggered via lp-size-guide.js).
{% endcomment %}

{{ 'lp-size-guide.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<section class="lp-sg" id="size-guide">
  <div class="lp-sg__inner">

    <p class="lp-sg__eyebrow">IL CONSIGLIO DEL DR. KAMPES</p>
    <h2 class="lp-sg__h2">TROVA LA TUA TAGLIA PERFETTA</h2>

    <ol class="lp-sg__steps">

      <li class="lp-sg__step">
        <div class="lp-sg__step-head">
          <span class="lp-sg__step-num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
          <div class="lp-sg__step-title-wrap">
            <h3 class="lp-sg__step-title">PRENDI UNA SOLETTA INTERNA</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="lp-sg__step-text">Rimuovi la soletta interna di una scarpa che usi abitualmente.</p>
        <div class="lp-sg__step-img">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/soletta.png?v=1777976336" alt="PRENDI UNA SOLETTA INTERNA" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="lp-sg__step">
        <div class="lp-sg__step-head">
          <span class="lp-sg__step-num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
          <div class="lp-sg__step-title-wrap">
            <h3 class="lp-sg__step-title">MISURA LA LUNGHEZZA</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="lp-sg__step-text">Misura la lunghezza della soletta da punta a tallone come indicato.</p>
        <div class="lp-sg__step-img">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/soletta_cm.png?v=1777976337" alt="MISURA LA LUNGHEZZA" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="lp-sg__step">
        <div class="lp-sg__step-head">
          <span class="lp-sg__step-num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
          <div class="lp-sg__step-title-wrap">
            <h3 class="lp-sg__step-title">TROVA LA TUA TAGLIA IN TABELLA</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="lp-sg__step-text">Usa la lunghezza in cm per trovare la tua taglia nella tabella qui sotto.</p>
        <div class="lp-sg__step-img">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/tabella.png?v=1777976337" alt="TROVA LA TUA TAGLIA IN TABELLA" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </li>

      <li class="lp-sg__step">
        <div class="lp-sg__step-head">
          <span class="lp-sg__step-num" aria-hidden="true">4</span>
          <div class="lp-sg__step-title-wrap">
            <h3 class="lp-sg__step-title">SCEGLI LA TUA TAGLIA PERFETTA</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="lp-sg__step-text">Scegli la taglia che corrisponde alla tua misura per il massimo comfort.</p>
        <div class="lp-sg__step-img">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/scarpa_profilo.png?v=1777976337" alt="SCEGLI LA TUA TAGLIA PERFETTA" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </li>

    </ol>

    <button type="button" class="lp-sg__back" data-lp-sg-open-popup>
      <span>Consulta la tabella taglie</span>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m13 6 6 6-6 6"/></svg>
    </button>

  </div>
</section>

<script src="{{ 'lp-size-guide.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
